<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes and no, it is a very good book and worth a read and is definitely meant as a critique on a colonial patriarchical society. Mostly it is just about<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes and no, it is a very good book and worth a read and is definitely meant as a critique on a colonial patriarchical society. Mostly it is just about the deep unhappiness that comes with not being able to live your life on your own terms.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
