          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;If she had been left alone she would have gone on, in her own way, enjoying herself thoroughly, until people found one day that she had turned imperceptibly into one of those women who have become old without ever having been middle aged: a little withered, a little acid, hard as nails, sentimentally kindhearted, and addicted to religion or small dogs.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
